Description:
    Creates a default AngularJS app

Example:
    yo angular-feature [--coffee] [--minsafe]

    This will create (division by component):
        Gruntfile.js
        bower.json

        app/index.html
        app/scripts/your-app-name-here.js
        app/scripts/controllers/main.js
        app/bower_components/angular/angular.js
        app/styles/main.css
        app/views/main.html

        test/lib/angular-mocks.js
        test/spec/controllers/main.js

    or (division by feature):
        Gruntfile.js
        bower.json

        app/src/common/views/index.html
        app/src/common/your-app-name-here.js
        app/src/common/controllers/main.js
        app/src/vendor/bower_components/angular/angular.js
        app/src/common/assets/styles/main.css
        app/src/common/views/main.html

        app/src/common/test/lib/angular-mocks.js
        app/src/common/test/spec/controllers/main.js

    Paths can by changed in a config.json file.

